---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
    <section class="py-20 lg:py-32">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
            <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-500 mb-12">Effective: January 10, 2026</p>

            <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
                <section class="mb-10">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">1. Definitions</h2>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-slate-400">
                        <li><strong class="text-slate-200">Service:</strong> The Inner Fire platform and related tools.</li>
                        <li><strong class="text-slate-200">Personal Data:</strong> Information identifying a living individual.</li>
                        <li><strong class="text-slate-200">Usage Data:</strong> Data collected automatically from interactions.</li>
                        <li><strong class="text-slate-200">User:</strong> Any individual accessing the Service.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-10">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">2. Information We Collect</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">We collect information to operate effectively.</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-slate-400">
                        <li><strong class="text-slate-200">Personal Data:</strong> Email, Username, Preferences.</li>
                        <li><strong class="text-slate-200">Usage Data:</strong> IP, Browser, Device info.</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-10">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">3. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400">We use cookies for functionality, security, and analytics. You may disable them in your browser, though some features may break.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-10">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">4. How We Use Data</h2>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-slate-400">
                        <li>Service maintenance and improvement.</li>
                        <li>Community features and progress tracking.</li>
                        <li>Security and fraud prevention.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 mt-4">We do not sell personal data.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-10">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">5. AI & Automation</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400">We may use AI to provide structured guidance. These systems do not replace professional advice.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-10">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">6. Data Retention</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400">We retain data only as long as necessary for legal and operational purposes.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-10">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">7. User Rights (GDPR)</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400">EEA residents have rights to access, correct, delete, or restrict processing of their data.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-10">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">8. Contact</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400">Questions? <a href="/contact" class="text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors font-bold">See our contact page</a>.</p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
